scripts.build: npm run clean && npx nx build:main supabase-js && npx nx build:module supabase-js && npx nx build:umd supabase-js
scripts.serve:coverage: npx nx test:coverage supabase-js && serve test/coverage
scripts.test: npx nx test:types supabase-js && npx nx test:run supabase-js
scripts.test:all: npx nx test:types supabase-js && npx nx test:run supabase-js && npx nx test:integration supabase-js && npx nx test:integration:browser supabase-js
scripts.test:bun: cd test/integration/bun && bun install && bun test
scripts.test:node:playwright: cd test/integration/node-browser && npm install && cp ../../../dist/umd/supabase.js . && npm run test
scripts.test:types: npx nx build:module supabase-js && tsd --files test/types/*.test-d.ts && jsr publish --dry-run --allow-dirty
scripts.update:test-deps: npx nx build supabase-js && npm pack && cp supabase-supabase-js-*.tgz test/integration/expo/supabase-supabase-js-0.0.0-automated.tgz && cp supabase-supabase-js-*.tgz test/integration/next/supabase-supabase-js-0.0.0-automated.tgz && cp supabase-supabase-js-*.tgz test/deno/supabase-supabase-js-0.0.0-automated.tgz && cp supabase-supabase-js-*.tgz test/integration/bun/supabase-supabase-js-0.0.0-automated.tgz && cd test/integration/expo && npm install && cd ../next && npm install --legacy-peer-deps && cd ../../deno && npm install && cd ../integration/bun && bun install
scripts.update:test-deps:bun: npx nx build supabase-js && npm pack && cp supabase-supabase-js-*.tgz test/integration/bun/supabase-supabase-js-0.0.0-automated.tgz && cd test/integration/bun && bun install
scripts.update:test-deps:deno: npx nx build supabase-js && npm pack && cp supabase-supabase-js-*.tgz test/deno/supabase-supabase-js-0.0.0-automated.tgz && cd test/deno && npm install
scripts.update:test-deps:expo: npx nx build supabase-js && npm pack && cp supabase-supabase-js-*.tgz test/integration/expo/supabase-supabase-js-0.0.0-automated.tgz && cd test/integration/expo && npm install
scripts.update:test-deps:next: npx nx build supabase-js && npm pack && cp supabase-supabase-js-*.tgz test/integration/next/supabase-supabase-js-0.0.0-automated.tgz && cd test/integration/next && npm install --legacy-peer-deps
